title: Batman - Li'l Gotham 016 (2013) (digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
description:
CBR | English | 24 pages

Batman Li'l Gotham #16
Written by Dustin Nguyen & Derek Fridolfs
Art by Dustin Nguyen

There are no holidays in August--at least until Alfred forces Batman to get out of Gotham for a few days. Bruce invites Selina to a tropical beach getaway, but with Catwoman sharing his yacht, buried treasure and pirates can't be too far behind!
